  "title": "All API Additions From Java 21 to 25",
  "summary": "Learn about all API additions between Java 21 and Java 25: scoped values, stream gatherers, class-file API, foreign function and memory API, Javadoc additions, and preview features.",
  "content": "<p>Learn about all API additions between Java 21 and Java 25: scoped values, stream gatherers, class-file API, foreign function and memory API, Javadoc additions, and preview features.</p><p>As is, this video&#x27;s script is way too confusing to work in written form and I am way too busy (read: &quot;lazy&quot;) to patch it up until it does, so I&#x27;m afraid, you&#x27;ll have to watch the video.\nHere are time-stamped links to each chapter together with all follow-up sources:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCaDlCZJydI&amp;t=0m00s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Intro</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCaDlCZJydI&amp;t=1m07s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Smaller Additions</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>CLDR Update: <a href=\"https://inside.java/2024/03/29/quality-heads-up/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Quality Heads-up</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://download.java.net/java/early_access/jdk25/docs/api/new-list.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">New APIs in Javadoc</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCaDlCZJydI&amp;t=3m57s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Scoped Values</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://openjdk.org/jeps/506\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEP 506</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7tfUJLUbZiM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IJN #86</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCaDlCZJydI&amp;t=9m22s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Stream Gatherers</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://openjdk.org/jeps/485\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEP 485</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jqUhObgDd5Q\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEP Cafe #23</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v_5SKpfkI2U\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Deep Dive with the Expert</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCaDlCZJydI&amp;t=15m54s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Class-File API</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://openjdk.org/jeps/484\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEP 484</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pcg-E_qyMOI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">A Classfile API for the JDK</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCaDlCZJydI&amp;t=19m44s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Foreign Function and Memory API</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://openjdk.org/jeps/454\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEP 454</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCaDlCZJydI&amp;t=23m03s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Javadoc Improvements</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://openjdk.org/jeps/413\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEP 413 (Snippets)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nipafx.dev//javadoc-snippets-maven/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Build Snippets with Maven</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://openjdk.org/jeps/467\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEP 467 (Markdown)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AvAIFq4fLPw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IJN #68</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCaDlCZJydI&amp;t=24m36s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Preview Features</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://openjdk.org/jeps/505\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEP 505 (Structured Concurrency)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://openjdk.org/jeps/502\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEP 502 (Stable Values)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://openjdk.org/jeps/470\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEP 470 (PEM)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Next Up</h2>\n<p>If you haven&#x27;t watched it yet, also check out this video on how to update to Java 25:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9azNjz7s1Ck\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Embedded video.</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCaDlCZJydI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Watch the video.</a></p>",
